{"tid":1957503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疾控中心終籲民眾戴口罩 特朗普：我未必跟","createTime":"2020-04-04T03:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T05:03:00.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"62388b8a6fe14eeb14f28080276e3d46da6026f1","tid":1957503,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"【美國疫情】疾控中心終籲民眾戴口罩 特朗普：我未必跟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國疫情惡化，新型冠狀病毒肺炎（新冠肺炎）確診個案已超27萬。美國疾控中心（CDC）一改早前所指，有病徵才需要戴口罩的說法，改為建議所有民眾外出時需戴口罩。美國總統特朗普表示，此指引僅屬建議性質，他自己則未必會跟從。<br />\n<br />\n美國疾控中心周五建議民眾外出以「非醫療級布料」（non-medical cloth）蒙面，呼籲民眾外出時可戴上布口罩掩蓋口鼻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2610352/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E7%96%BE%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%B5%82%E7%B1%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%20%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E8%B7%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2610352%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2596%25BE%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%25B5%2582%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%2520%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%25B7%259F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQymWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=9ed77833\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2610352/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E7%96%BE%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%B5%82%E7%B1%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%20%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E8%B7%9F</a>"},{"pid":"173debdd65d8d87a8d5fbace49d87f07a1b095cf","tid":1957503,"uid":291405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OHnxkh1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOHnxkh1.png&h=dad93e7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06672f0b4de81e682c4a1fd67421b89faffa12e0","tid":1957503,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"疾控中心建議，民眾亦可以選擇用T恤、圍巾、手帕等掩蓋口鼻，而醫療級口罩如N95等則留給前線醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rU4br8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rU4br8.jpg&h=769d45c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a1bed8896ec7b3ab9de8057373aa57e614e8332","tid":1957503,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"侵侵又撚狗 等睇真心"},{"pid":"9038d040c75b50d4d74bc1f00de511acebc4c731","tid":1957503,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:03:00.000Z","msg":"廢老侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}